Here are the simplifications (assuming \(y\ge0\) and \(n\ge0\) so that we can pull out even powers):

a) 
\[
(\sqrt{15y})(\sqrt{5y^3})
=\sqrt{15y\cdot5y^3}
=\sqrt{75\,y^4}
=\sqrt{25\cdot3\;y^4}
=5\,y^2\sqrt3.
\]

b)
\[
(\sqrt{2n^2})(\sqrt{18n^3})
=\sqrt{2n^2\cdot18n^3}
=\sqrt{36\,n^5}
=\sqrt{36\;n^4\;n}
=6\,n^2\sqrt n.
\]
